<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Tulis - Luapin Aja</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=swap" name="viewport" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
<script src="https://challenges.cloudflare.com/turnstile/v0/api.js" async defer></script>
<style>
    body { font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; background: #f0f2f5; }
    .glass-nav { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
    .social-card { background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
    .material-symbols-outlined { font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24; vertical-align: middle; }
    .icon-fill { font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1; }
</style>
</head>
<body class="text-slate-800 flex flex-col min-h-screen" oncontextmenu="return false;">

<nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 glass-nav">
<div class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto flex justify-between items-center h-14 px-4">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <a href="/jelajah" class="p-2 hover:bg-slate-100 rounded-full transition-colors">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-600">arrow_back</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 group">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-indigo-600 icon-fill text-[28px]">psychology_alt</span>
            <span class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tighter">Luapin Aja</span>
        </a>
    </div>
</div>
</nav>

<main class="flex-grow pt-20 pb-24 px-4 max-w-[680px] w-full mx-auto">
<div class="social-card p-6 md:p-8">
    <header class="mb-8 border-b border-slate-100 pb-6">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">Tulis Pesan Anonim</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium">Bagikan apa yang mengganjal di pikiranmu tanpa ragu.</p>
    </header>

    <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined' && error === 'captcha') { %>
        <div class="bg-rose-50 text-rose-600 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl mb-6 text-xs font-bold border border-rose-100 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">warning</span> Mohon verifikasi bahwa Anda manusia!
        </div>
    <% } %>

    <form action="/tulis" method="POST" class="space-y-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="space-y-2">
                <label class="text-[11px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 ml-1">Nama Samaran (Opsional)</label>
                <input type="text" name="pengirim" placeholder="Boleh dikosongkan (Anonim)" class="w-full bg-slate-50 border-none rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none transition-all">
                <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 ml-1 italic">*Identitasmu tetap rahasia meski diisi.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-2">
                <label class="text-[11px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 ml-1">Kategori</label>
                <div class="relative">
                    <select name="category" required class="w-full appearance-none bg-slate-50 border-none rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none cursor-pointer">
                        <option value="Tanpa Kategori">Tanpa Kategori</option>
                        <option value="Rahasia Pribadi">Rahasia Pribadi</option>
                        <option value="Cinta & Asmara">Cinta & Asmara</option>
                        <option value="Keluarga">Keluarga</option>
                        <option value="Pertemanan">Pertemanan</option>
                        <option value="Penyesalan">Penyesalan</option>
                    </select>
                    <div class="absolute right-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none text-slate-400">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">expand_more</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="text-[11px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 ml-1">Pesan Kamu</label>
            <textarea name="message" required class="w-full bg-slate-50 border-none rounded-2xl px-4 py-4 text-[16px] font-medium text-slate-800 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none placeholder:text-slate-300 resize-none" placeholder="Apa yang ingin kamu luapkan?" rows="6"></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-center py-2">
            <div class="cf-turnstile" data-sitekey="0x4AAAAAADC6MSMP3c413MWX" data-theme="light"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-2">
            <button class="w-full py-3 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white font-bold text-sm rounded-full shadow-md transition-all active:scale-95" type="submit">
                Kirim Pengakuan
            </button>
        </div>
    </form>
</div>

<div class="mt-6 text-center">
    <a href="/jelajah" class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-1">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">explore</span> Lihat kiriman orang lain
    </a>
</div>
</main>

<footer class="w-full text-center py-8 text-slate-400 mt-auto">
    <p class="text-[11px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">Copyright &copy; 2026 AP. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
